{"TopicId":191448,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"So, ksp 1.9...","CreatedByName":"Cristiano Kerman","CreatedById":202675,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-06T12:25:20Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Cristiano Kerman","CreatedById":202675,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-06T12:25:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI love this game, but I have a question for 1.9, I want to give you an idea, ksp don\u2019t have a multiple colors for the pieces, but I want to create my colors and my livrees, it\u2019s possible in 1.9?\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nps. Sorry for my English but I\u2019m italian\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Val","CreatedById":126227,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-06T13:11:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003EMoved from KSP2 discussion.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-06T13:26:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223737013\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022191448\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221580991920\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022202675\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Cristiano Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n59 minutes ago, Cristiano Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI love this game, but I have a question for 1.9, I want to give you an idea, ksp don\u2019t have a multiple colors for the pieces, but I want to create my colors and my livrees, it\u2019s possible in 1.9?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt can be done by modding. It almost certainly won\u0027t be in the base game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-06T14:35:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is, however, confirmed for KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DeadJohn","CreatedById":201293,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-02-06T16:47:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s unlikely that much color switching will be added to 1.9. You\u0027ll need mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow much color switching do you want? Restock changes the artwork for standard parts and supports more white/dark/orange color switching. Link below. There are other mods that allow more color changes but I haven\u0027t used them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnother option could be to keep stock colors, maybe mostly white parts, and attach flag/sticker/decal graphics. You could edit those graphics outside KSP to be any color. See Decalc\u0027o\u0027mania link below.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002283952\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5184776937\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/182679-18x-restock-revamping-ksps-art-january-12th-2020/\u0026amp;tab=comments\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=3552725\u0026amp;embedComment=3552725\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment#comment-3552725\u0022 style=\u0022height:299px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u0022190783\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6925331125\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/177940-18x-decalcomania/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:214px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}